    TWD, TZS, UAH, UGX, USD, USN, UYI, UYU, UZS, VEF, VND, VUV, WST, XAF, XAG, XAU, XBA, XBB,
    XBC, XBD, XCD, XDR, XOF, XPD, XPF, XPT, XSU, XTS, XUA, XXX, YER, ZAR, ZMW, ZWL
  ];
